<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Penetration Test Report - {{ engagement.target }}</title>
<style>
    @page {
        size: A4;
        margin: 2cm;
        @top-right { content: "CONFIDENTIAL"; font-size: 8pt; color: #999; }
        @bottom-center { content: "Page " counter(page) " of " counter(pages); font-size: 8pt; color: #999; }
    }

    :root {
        --critical: #dc2626;
        --high: #ea580c;
        --medium: #d97706;
        --low: #2563eb;
        --info: #6b7280;
        --bg: #0a0a0a;
        --surface: #111111;
        --surface-2: #1a1a1a;
        --border: #2a2a2a;
        --text: #e0e0e0;
        --text-muted: #888;
        --accent: #00ff88;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
        font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .cover {
        page-break-after: always;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 90vh;
        text-align: center;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 4rem;
    }

    .cover h1 {
        font-size: 28pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .cover .subtitle {
        font-size: 14pt;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .cover-meta {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto auto;
        gap: 0.5rem 2rem;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 11pt;
    }

    .cover-meta dt { color: var(--text-muted); }
    .cover-meta dd { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }

    .cover .confidential {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
        border: 2px solid var(--critical);
        color: var(--critical);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 12pt;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 16pt;
        color: var(--accent);
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
        page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    h3 {
        font-size: 12pt;
        color: var(--text);
        margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
        page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    p { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }

    .risk-banner {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        border: 2px solid;
        font-size: 14pt;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .risk-critical { border-color: var(--critical); color: var(--critical); background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1); }
    .risk-high { border-color: var(--high); color: var(--high); background: rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.1); }
    .risk-medium { border-color: var(--medium); color: var(--medium); background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1); }
    .risk-low { border-color: var(--low); color: var(--low); background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1); }

    .metrics-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .metric-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .metric-card .value {
        font-size: 24pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .metric-card .label {
        font-size: 8pt;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .severity-bar {
        display: flex;
        height: 32px;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .severity-bar div {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 8pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: white;
        min-width: 30px;
    }

    .sev-critical { background: var(--critical); }
    .sev-high { background: var(--high); }
    .sev-medium { background: var(--medium); }
    .sev-low { background: var(--low); }
    .sev-info { background: var(--info); }

    table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        font-size: 9pt;
    }

    th {
        background: var(--surface);
        color: var(--accent);
        text-align: left;
        padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        font-weight: 600;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: 8pt;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    td {
        padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        vertical-align: top;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--surface); }

    .finding-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-left: 4px solid;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .finding-card.critical { border-left-color: var(--critical); }
    .finding-card.high { border-left-color: var(--high); }
    .finding-card.medium { border-left-color: var(--medium); }
    .finding-card.low { border-left-color: var(--low); }
    .finding-card.info { border-left-color: var(--info); }

    .finding-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .finding-title {
        font-size: 11pt;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .severity-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
        font-size: 8pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        color: white;
    }

    .badge-critical { background: var(--critical); }
    .badge-high { background: var(--high); }
    .badge-medium { background: var(--medium); }
    .badge-low { background: var(--low); }
    .badge-info { background: var(--info); }

    .finding-meta {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
        gap: 0.25rem 1rem;
        font-size: 9pt;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    .finding-meta dt { color: var(--text-muted); }

    .remediation {
        background: var(--surface-2);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 9pt;
    }

    .remediation-label {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 8pt;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .chain-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .chain-steps {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0.75rem 0;
    }

    .chain-steps li {
        position: relative;
        padding: 0.5rem 0 0.5rem 2rem;
        border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
        margin-left: 0.5rem;
    }

    .chain-steps li::before {
        content: attr(data-step);
        position: absolute;
        left: -0.75rem;
        top: 0.4rem;
        width: 1.5rem;
        height: 1.5rem;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: var(--bg);
        font-size: 8pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .detection-rule {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 1rem;
        margin: 0.75rem 0;
        page-break-inside: avoid;
    }

    .detection-rule pre {
        background: var(--bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 0.75rem;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
        font-size: 8pt;
        overflow-x: auto;
        white-space: pre-wrap;
        word-wrap: break-word;
        color: var(--accent);
    }

    .detection-format {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: var(--bg);
        font-size: 7pt;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .toc { page-break-after: always; }
    .toc ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .toc li { padding: 0.3rem 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--border); }
    .toc a { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }

    .footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 1rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 8pt;
    }

    @media print {
        body { background: white; color: #111; }
        .cover, .finding-card, .chain-card, .detection-rule, .metric-card, th, tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: #f8f8f8;
        }
        :root {
            --accent: #0d9488;
            --border: #ddd;
            --text: #111;
            --text-muted: #666;
        }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Cover Page -->
<div class="cover">
    <h1>Penetration Test Report</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Security Assessment Findings</p>

    <dl class="cover-meta">
        <dt>Target</dt>
        <dd>{{ engagement.target }}</dd>
        <dt>Scope</dt>
        <dd>{{ engagement.scope | upper }}</dd>
        <dt>Date</dt>
        <dd>{{ date }}</dd>
        <dt>Status</dt>
        <dd>{{ engagement.status | title }}</dd>
        <dt>Findings</dt>
        <dd>{{ summary.total_findings }}</dd>
        <dt>Attack Chains</dt>
        <dd>{{ summary.attack_chains }}</dd>
    </dl>

    <div class="confidential">CONFIDENTIAL</div>
</div>

<!-- Table of Contents -->
<div class="toc">
    <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="#executive-summary">1. Executive Summary</a></li>
        <li><a href="#risk-overview">2. Risk Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#findings">3. Detailed Findings ({{ findings | length }})</a></li>
        {% if chains %}<li><a href="#attack-chains">4. Attack Chains ({{ chains | length }})</a></li>{% endif %}
        {% if detection_rules %}<li><a href="#detection-rules">5. Detection Rules ({{ detection_rules | length }})</a></li>{% endif %}
        <li><a href="#remediation">6. Remediation Roadmap</a></li>
        <li><a href="#methodology">7. Methodology</a></li>
    </ul>
</div>

<!-- Executive Summary -->
<h2 id="executive-summary">1. Executive Summary</h2>

<div class="risk-banner risk-{{ risk_level | lower }}">
    OVERALL RISK: {{ risk_level }}
</div>

<p>
    A penetration test was conducted against <strong>{{ engagement.target }}</strong> to identify
    security vulnerabilities and assess the application's security posture. The assessment
    followed OWASP Testing Guide v4 methodology and PTES standards.
</p>

<p>
    The assessment identified <strong>{{ summary.total_findings }}</strong> findings across
    {{ summary.by_severity | length }} severity levels, with
    <strong>{{ summary.by_severity.get('critical', 0) + summary.by_severity.get('high', 0) }}</strong>
    requiring immediate attention.
</p>

<!-- Risk Overview -->
<h2 id="risk-overview">2. Risk Overview</h2>

<div class="metrics-grid">
    <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="value" style="color: var(--critical)">{{ summary.by_severity.get('critical', 0) }}</div>
        <div class="label">Critical</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="value" style="color: var(--high)">{{ summary.by_severity.get('high', 0) }}</div>
        <div class="label">High</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="value" style="color: var(--medium)">{{ summary.by_severity.get('medium', 0) }}</div>
        <div class="label">Medium</div>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <div class="value" style="color: var(--low)">{{ summary.by_severity.get('low', 0) + summary.by_severity.get('info', 0) }}</div>
        <div class="label">Low / Info</div>
    </div>
</div>

{% set total = summary.total_findings or 1 %}
<div class="severity-bar">
    {% for sev, color in [('critical', 'critical'), ('high', 'high'), ('medium', 'medium'), ('low', 'low'), ('info', 'info')] %}
    {% set count = summary.by_severity.get(sev, 0) %}
    {% if count > 0 %}
    <div class="sev-{{ color }}" style="width: {{ (count / total * 100) | round(1) }}%">{{ count }}</div>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
</div>

<table>
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Severity</th>
            <th>Count</th>
            <th>Percentage</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        {% for sev in ['critical', 'high', 'medium', 'low', 'info'] %}
        {% set count = summary.by_severity.get(sev, 0) %}
        <tr>
            <td><span class="severity-badge badge-{{ sev }}">{{ sev }}</span></td>
            <td>{{ count }}</td>
            <td>{{ (count / total * 100) | round(1) }}%</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>

<!-- Detailed Findings -->
<h2 id="findings">3. Detailed Findings</h2>

{% for finding in findings %}
<div class="finding-card {{ finding.severity }}">
    <div class="finding-header">
        <span class="finding-title">{{ finding.title }}</span>
        <span class="severity-badge badge-{{ finding.severity }}">{{ finding.severity }}</span>
    </div>

    <p>{{ finding.description }}</p>

    <dl class="finding-meta">
        <dt>Target</dt><dd>{{ finding.target }}</dd>
        <dt>Category</dt><dd>{{ finding.category }}</dd>
        <dt>Tool</dt><dd>{{ finding.tool_source or 'N/A' }}</dd>
        {% if finding.cve %}<dt>CVE</dt><dd>{{ finding.cve }}</dd>{% endif %}
        {% if finding.cvss_score %}<dt>CVSS</dt><dd>{{ finding.cvss_score }}</dd>{% endif %}
    </dl>

    {% if finding.evidence %}
    <dl class="finding-meta">
        <dt>Evidence</dt><dd>{{ finding.evidence }}</dd>
    </dl>
    {% endif %}

    {% if finding.remediation %}
    <div class="remediation">
        <div class="remediation-label">Remediation</div>
        {{ finding.remediation }}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>
{% endfor %}

<!-- Attack Chains -->
{% if chains %}
<h2 id="attack-chains">4. Attack Chains</h2>

<p>Attack chains correlate individual findings into multi-step attack paths that demonstrate
business impact beyond what any single finding shows alone.</p>

{% for chain in chains %}
<div class="chain-card">
    <div class="finding-header">
        <span class="finding-title">{{ chain.name }}</span>
        <span class="severity-badge badge-{{ chain.severity }}">{{ chain.severity }}</span>
    </div>

    <p>{{ chain.description or chain.impact }}</p>
    <p><strong>Impact:</strong> {{ chain.impact }}</p>

    <ol class="chain-steps">
        {% for step in chain.steps %}
        <li data-step="{{ loop.index }}">{{ step.action or step.get('finding_id', '') }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ol>
</div>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

<!-- Detection Rules -->
{% if detection_rules %}
<h2 id="detection-rules">5. Detection Rules</h2>

<p>The following detection rules were generated to help your SOC identify similar attacks.
Rules are provided in Sigma, Splunk SPL, and Microsoft Sentinel KQL formats.</p>

{% for rule in detection_rules %}
<div class="detection-rule">
    <span class="detection-format">{{ rule.format }}</span>
    <strong>{{ rule.description }}</strong>
    <pre>{{ rule.rule }}</pre>
</div>
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

<!-- Remediation Roadmap -->
<h2 id="remediation">6. Remediation Roadmap</h2>

<h3>Priority 1: Immediate (0-7 days)</h3>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Severity</th><th>Finding</th><th>Target</th><th>Remediation</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
    {% set ns = namespace(idx=0) %}
    {% for f in findings if f.severity in ['critical', 'high'] %}
    {% set ns.idx = ns.idx + 1 %}
    <tr>
        <td>{{ ns.idx }}</td>
        <td><span class="severity-badge badge-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity }}</span></td>
        <td>{{ f.title }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.target }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.remediation or 'See finding details' }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% else %}
    <tr><td colspan="5" style="text-align:center; color: var(--text-muted)">No critical or high severity findings</td></tr>
    {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Priority 2: Short-term (7-30 days)</h3>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Finding</th><th>Target</th><th>Remediation</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
    {% set ns = namespace(idx=0) %}
    {% for f in findings if f.severity == 'medium' %}
    {% set ns.idx = ns.idx + 1 %}
    <tr>
        <td>{{ ns.idx }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.title }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.target }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.remediation or 'See finding details' }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% else %}
    <tr><td colspan="4" style="text-align:center; color: var(--text-muted)">No medium severity findings</td></tr>
    {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Priority 3: Planned (30-90 days)</h3>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Finding</th><th>Target</th><th>Remediation</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
    {% set ns = namespace(idx=0) %}
    {% for f in findings if f.severity in ['low', 'info'] %}
    {% set ns.idx = ns.idx + 1 %}
    <tr>
        <td>{{ ns.idx }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.title }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.target }}</td>
        <td>{{ f.remediation or 'See finding details' }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
</table>

<!-- Methodology -->
<h2 id="methodology">7. Methodology</h2>

<p>The assessment was conducted using pentest-ai with the following phases:</p>

<table>
    <thead><tr><th>Phase</th><th>Description</th><th>Tools</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td>1. Reconnaissance</td><td>Service enumeration, DNS, port scanning</td><td>nmap, subfinder, builtin scanners</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2. Vulnerability Scanning</td><td>Automated vulnerability detection</td><td>nuclei, nikto, sqlmap, builtin scanners</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3. Deduplication</td><td>SHA-256 fingerprinting, CWE/OWASP mapping</td><td>pentest-ai dedup engine</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4. Chain Discovery</td><td>Multi-step attack path correlation</td><td>pentest-ai chain engine</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5. Detection Engineering</td><td>Sigma, SPL, KQL rule generation</td><td>pentest-ai detection engine</td></tr>
        <tr><td>6. Evidence Collection</td><td>SHA-256 integrity-verified artifact storage</td><td>pentest-ai evidence engine</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<div class="footer">
    Generated by pentest-ai on {{ date }} | CONFIDENTIAL
</div>

</body>
</html>
